comment: Earthly as in “mortal”, opposed to Heavenly and “immortal”
Left is Earthly as opposed to Heavenly life, right is less explicitly about that religious connection

This is a very fine distinction: left means Earthly in contrast to religious, with a positive lean on Earthly. Whereas right sees the opposite. The relation is clear, but the difference in intent should supply a difference in perception too.
Right is “life-on-earth”, Left is “power-on-Earth”, as opposed to heavenly power
